'''Charles Rocket''' ([[August 24]], [[1940s|1949]]–[[October 7]], [[2005]]) voiced the [[Feeorin/Legends|Feeorin]] [[Nym/Legends|Nym]] in [[Star Wars: Starfighter (video game)|''Star Wars: Starfighter'']] and ''[[Star Wars: Jedi Starfighter]]''. He was credited as '''Charlie Rocket''' in both games.

Rocket was also known as the villain Nicholas Andre in the film ''[[Wikipedia:Dumb and Dumber|Dumb and Dumber]]''.

